---
import ServiceLayout from "../layouts/ServiceLayout.astro";
const phoneNumber = import.meta.env.PHONE_NUMBER;
---

<ServiceLayout
    title="24 Hour Mobile Tyre Fitting | Tyre Emergency Ltd"
    description="Flat tyre? Tyre Emergency provides quick, reliable, 24-hour mobile tyre fitting in Nottinghamshire. Call now and get back on the road fast."
    heading="Need a Tyre? We'll Come to You!"
    tagline="Our mobile tyre fitters will come to you at home, work or roadside. Give us a call now for immediate assistance."
    backgroundUrl="/img/24-hour-mobile-tyre-fitting-service.webp"
>
    <h1 class="fw-bold mb-0">Welcome to Tyre Emergency</h1>
    <h2 class="text-danger mb-3">Your Local 24Hr Mobile Tyre Service in Nottinghamshire</h2>
    <p><em><span class="fw-bold">If you’ve got a flat tyre, we can help.</span> Tyre Emergency comes straight to you, wherever you are, to get your tyre sorted quickly—often in less than an hour.</em></p>
    <p>We provide 24-hour mobile tyre fitting across Nottinghamshire. Whether you’re at home, at work, or stuck by the roadside, we’ll handle everything from puncture repairs to replacing your tyre. Our goal is to get you moving again safely and without hassle.</p>

    <h2 class="fw-bold">Where We Work</h2>
    <p>We serve Nottinghamshire and nearby areas, including Nottingham, Mansfield, Worksop, and Newark-on-Trent. Not sure if we can reach you? Just give us a call to find out.</p>

    <h2 class="fw-bold">Why Choose Us</h2>
    <p>We understand how frustrating a flat tyre can be, which is why we aim to reach you quickly—usually in under an hour, no matter the time of day. With over ten years of experience, we’re confident in our ability to fix the problem and get you back on the road. Plus, our pricing is always clear, with no hidden surprises.</p>

    <h2 class="fw-bold">Call Us Today</h2>
    <p>Getting help is easy. Call us now at <a href=`tel:${phoneNumber}` class="link-danger">{phoneNumber}</a>, let us know your tyre details and location, and we’ll provide a quote and let you know how soon we’ll arrive. Don’t let a flat tyre ruin your plans—Tyre Emergency is here to help, 24/7.</p>
</ServiceLayout>
